Headers (Internal):

string.h - provides sprintf2, which prints into a dynamically allocated
    std::string object.
atomic_gpu.h - provides atomicAdd(double*, double) to emulate double-precision
    atomics for CUDA architectures prior to Pascal.
cuerr.h - provides CUERR; macro to be placed after synchronous CUDA calls to
    check for errors and print/die if any are found.

Implementation:

string.cpp - sprintf2 implementation
